803
00:39:27,432 --> 00:39:28,832
we're all
out of our element.

804
00:39:28,834 --> 00:39:30,734
- I don't know how much
that's true.

805
00:39:30,736 --> 00:39:32,836
- Still, as much as I thought
our project's implications

