00:41:52,577 --> 00:41:56,212
Surely some duty ought
to be paid to that reality.

875
00:41:56,214 --> 00:41:58,615
- That's only the beginning.

876
00:41:58,617 --> 00:42:00,850
- There's a war
being waged in cyberspace,

877
