00:42:49,200 --> 00:42:52,268
because it, uh, it unlocks
and categorizes things

901
00:42:52,270 --> 00:42:53,803
that the mind
can't possibly understand.

902
00:42:53,805 --> 00:42:55,805
I-I don't expect you to
at this point.

903
00:42:55,807 --> 00:42:58,775
But there are certain
foundational proofs, okay,

904
00:42:58,777 --> 00:43:00,810
that lead
to more powerful conclusions.

905
00:43:00,812 --> 00:43:04,948
To lock this away so you
can spy on somebody is criminal.

906
00:43:04,950 --> 00:43:06,316
- Oh, that is so ignorant
and condescending

907
00:43:06,318 --> 00:43:07,917
it makes me want to spit.

908
00:43:07,919 --> 00:43:09,352
This was the most important
unsolved problem

909
00:43:09,354 --> 00:43:11,120
in computer science.

910
00:43:11,122 --> 00:43:13,289
To think you were the only
mathematicians in the world

911
00:43:13,291 --> 00:43:15,892
focusing your efforts on this
is naive.

912
00:43:15,894 --> 00:43:18,061
You're pawns, automatons.

913
00:43:18,063 --> 00:43:20,263
We funded you.
We brought you together.

914
00:43:20,265 --> 00:43:22,298
You were denied nothing.
Thought was fostered,

915
00:43:22,300 --> 00:43:24,734
and, ultimately,
a solution was achieved.

916
00:43:24,736 --> 00:43:26,235
You were a piece
of the puzzle.

917
00:43:26,237 --> 00:43:28,905
A cog.
Separately, you're nothing.

918
00:43:28,907 --> 00:43:31,307
You were the people
we mocked growing up.

919
00:43:31,309 --> 00:43:33,209
But collectively,
you have altered world history

920
00:43:33,211 --> 00:43:37,313
and put the proper power
in the proper hands.

921
00:43:37,315 --> 00:43:41,317
But don't forget your origin.
You were made.

922
00:43:41,319 --> 00:43:46,155
A soldered link
in a greater chain reaction.

923
00:43:50,995 --> 00:43:55,131
- [Grunting]
9, 10, 11, 12,

