00:45:56,221 --> 00:45:59,355
well beyond
the pythagorean theorem here,

962
00:45:59,357 --> 00:46:01,090
I would say it's, uh,

963
00:46:01,092 --> 00:46:03,392
a system that
provides solutions

964
00:46:03,394 --> 00:46:05,161
