the answer with its hoof.

1005
00:48:20,465 --> 00:48:22,398
So we called in experts
and researchers

1006
00:48:22,400 --> 00:48:23,499
to look at the horse,

1007
00:48:23,501 --> 00:48:25,635
and they were fascinated
by him.

1008
00:48:25,637 --> 00:48:27,336
As they tested him,
they found out

1009
